plato_targets.csv: 
	Plato asPIC IDs crossmatched with Gaia data, classified into thin disc (2), thick disc (1), and halo (0). 
	By Akshara (v March 24th 2024).

	Columns added:
	- num_CCD: added using the code in notebook 01_plato_targets
	- mh_xgboost: [Fe/H] metallicities based on Gaia low-resolution XP spectrophotometry
	- mh_gspspec: [Fe/H] metallicities based on Gaia RVS medium-resolution spectra
	- alphafe_gspspec: [alpha/Fe] based on Gaia RVS medium-resolution spectra

	The original data is found in the Kapteyn intranet (kapteyn.astro.rug.nl):
	net/gaia2/data/users/viswanathan/plato-exoplanets
	Files:
	- gaia_columns_plato_targets_classified_vMar24.csv
	- gaia_columns_plato_targets_classified_vMar24_feh_andrae.csv (mh_xgboost column)
	- gaia_columns_plato_targets_classified_vMar24_gspspec_alpha_fe.csv (mh_xgboost, alphafe_gspspec columns)

plato_targets_LOPS2.csv: 
Subselection of plato_targets in LOPS field (num_CCD_LOPS2 > 0)
